00:14:17.520 --> 00:14:21.760
but what it can do is fold back on
itself and, thereby,

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:40.320
put these atoms into a regular
arrangement.

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:14.200
This is now forming a zone of

00:14:14.200 --> 00:14:18.600
