It is going to be flexible because

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:13.490
what are the only bonds operative
here? They are just weak Van der

00:15:13.490 --> 00:15:17.830
Waals bonds, mechanically flexible.
It is high band-gap material and it

00:15:17.830 --> 00:15:22.750
