That is low-density polyethylene.

00:15:39.250 --> 00:15:44.750
High-density polyethylene, well, it
has some zones of this.

00:15:44.750 --> 00:15:50.250
The high-density polyethylene has
these near crystalline zones,

00:15:50.250 --> 00:15:55.070
and then it is broadly amorphous.
The difference here is small.

00:15:55.070 --> 00:15:59.210
The density here is about 0.92
